  3.779105592893746*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a0b95b74-2156-4cc5-97da-\
127143a869d0"],

Cell["\<\
The classifier fits very well the data but it is not generic in the sense \
that it will typically not predict well the class of new data.\
\>", "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.778918975876884*^9, 3.778918992044814*^9}, {
  3.7789190606382713`*^9, 3.778919063510209*^9}, {3.7789191059348793`*^9, 
  3.778919196560604*^9}, {3.7791052676466837`*^9, 3.7791052733671*^9}, {
  3.779105593700094*^9, 
  3.779105633237453*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"81963059-d83f-4da5-ac4f-\
b95d02d41a07"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The model is ",
 StyleBox["simpler for larger values of ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 StyleBox["k",
  FontWeight->"Bold",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ": The nearest neighbours do not change so much as we classify new samples."
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.778918975876884*^9, 3.778918992044814*^9}, {
  3.7789190606382713`*^9, 3.778919063510209*^9}, {3.7789191059348793`*^9, 
  3.778919131039569*^9}, {3.779104883304051*^9, 3.779104932753964*^9}, {
  3.779104972370706*^9, 
  3.779105020682426*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8dba4cb9-913f-4a20-ba62-\
93e1fe285efd"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In the ",
 StyleBox["extreme case",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " in which ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"k", "=", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["N", "1"], "+", 
     SubscriptBox["N", "2"]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "771f783f-719e-46b7-a4ef-c8500162188f"],
 " (i.e. we use as many neighbours as data points), the prediction would be \
identical for any new sample. ",
 StyleBox["Bad...",
  FontWeight->"Bold"]
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.778918975876884*^9, 3.778918992044814*^9}, {
  3.7789190606382713`*^9, 3.778919063510209*^9}, {3.7789191059348793`*^9, 
  3.778919131039569*^9}, {3.779104883304051*^9, 3.779104948201152*^9}, {
  3.779105028084216*^9, 3.779105057236689*^9}, {3.779105116870103*^9, 
  3.779105202030182*^9}, {3.779105656237776*^9, 3.7791056562402973`*^9}, {
  3.77910569903864*^9, 
  3.779105701670212*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"abd87ba9-ee3b-4a07-a2ff-\
b06cb0063bbd"]
}, Open  ]],

