Cell["\<\
Of course, for Min-Max normalization, one could use the formula straight away:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8139329279590178`*^9, 
  3.8139329497615037`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a25fbe00-ab38-4cb5-b789-\
5d2e0bdc3579"],

